                     <interp inst="t18220522-43-person402" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . There had been a load of clover there just before the prisoner came; there are thirty-six trusses in the load - I counted them and found only thirty-four.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. When I entered the yard, Hankin had half filled his cart - as I was going away they said I had a truss; I said it was unknown to me.</p>
